OL,3,CWildfire destroys area of ancient
OL,4,Cwoodland
OL,6,FA wildfire has destroyed part of an
OL,7,Fancient woodland in East Sussex.
OL,9,FFirefighters were called to reports of
OL,10,Fa blaze at Abbots Wood, near
OL,11,FArlington, on Monday afternoon.
OL,13,FIt took hold of an area of gorse and
OL,14,Ftrees, measuring around 600 metres by
OL,15,F200 metres.
OL,17,FThe fire was brought under control in
OL,18,Fthe late evening, with some
OL,19,Ffirefighters remaining on the scene
OL,20,Fovernight to monitor for hotspots.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
