OL,3,CWildfire destroys area of ancient
OL,4,Cwoodland
OL,6,FEight fire appliances were in
OL,7,Fattendance at the height of the fire.
OL,8,FThe were assisted by local farmers who
OL,9,Fdampened down areas to prevent it from
OL,10,Fspreading.
